Alexis GONZALEZ, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Mariana TORRES, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-1144 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 13, 2018 SUAREZ, LOGUE and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.
